name: Web
body:
### Welcome to my personal GitHub Page.
I compiled a few list of projects you might find useful:

### Privacy
`freelan` [https://github.com/freelan-developers/freelan-all](https://github.com/freelan-developers/freelan-all)

`syncthing` [https://github.com/syncthing/syncthing](https://github.com/syncthing/syncthing)

`TextSecure` [https://github.com/WhisperSystems/TextSecure](https://github.com/WhisperSystems/TextSecure)

`crypto` [https://github.com/chrissimpkins/crypto](https://github.com/chrissimpkins/crypto)

### Media
`airplayer` [https://github.com/Tomohiro/airplayer](https://github.com/Tomohiro/airplayer)

`clicktoplugin` [https://github.com/hoyois/clicktoplugin](https://github.com/hoyois/clicktoplugin)

### Computer Graphics, Modeling and Visualization
`libigl` [https://github.com/libigl/libigl](https://github.com/libigl/libigl)

`libQEx` [https://github.com/hcebke/libQEx](https://github.com/hcebke/libQEx)

`IA-FEMesh` [https://github.com/ctpr/IA-FEMesh](https://github.com/ctpr/IA-FEMesh)

`mapclient` [https://github.com/MusculoskeletalAtlasProject/mapclient](https://github.com/MusculoskeletalAtlasProject/mapclient)

`pydicom` [https://github.com/darcymason/pydicom](https://github.com/darcymason/pydicom)

`VMTK` [https://github.com/vmtk/vmtk](https://github.com/vmtk/vmtk)

`SimBody` [https://github.com/simbody/simbody](https://github.com/simbody/simbody)

`PCL` [https://github.com/PointCloudLibrary/pcl](https://github.com/PointCloudLibrary/pcl)

`CGAL` [https://github.com/CGAL/cgal](https://github.com/CGAL/cgal)

### Scientific Research
`Apple ResearchKit` [https://github.com/ResearchKit/ResearchKit](https://github.com/ResearchKit/ResearchKit)

### Interesting Organisations and Authors on Github
WhisperSystems (@WhisperSystems)
The Syncthing Project (@syncthing)
Lavabit (@lavabit)
The Musculoskeletal Atlas Project (@MusculoskeletalAtlasProject)
VTMK (@VMTK)
SimBody (@simbody)
Linus Torvalds (@torvalds)
Jakob Borg (@calmh)
Chris Simpkins (@chrissimpkins)
